; Coverage for commodity.cc date comparison in compare_by_commodity
; Two lots with same price but different dates forces the date comparison path
; The earlier date sorts first

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01]
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Buy More
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/02/01]
    Assets:Checking

test bal --lots Assets:Brokerage
10 AAPL {$150} [2024/01/01]
5 AAPL {$150} [2024/02/01]  Assets:Brokerage
end test
